%p
  SixNines is a free 24x7 monitor of your website
  availability. Just login, add one of your endpoints,
  and in a few minutes you get a detailed report.
  We ping all websites every minute.

%form{:method=>'get', :action=>'/'}
  %fieldset
    %input{:type=>'text', :name=>'q', :value=>query}
    %button{:type=>'submit'}>Search

- if query
  %p
    Found by
    ='"' + query + '":'
  - if found.empty?
    %p
      Nothing! Sorry about that.
  - else
    %ul
      - found.each do |e|
        %li
          =EpUri.new(e).to_html
          =EpBadge.new(e).to_html

- if !flips.empty?
  %p
    Recent flips:
  %ul
    - flips.each do |e|
      %li
        =EpUri.new(e).to_html
        =EpBadge.new(e).to_html
        =EpState.new(e).to_html
        =e.to_h['flipped']

